node.text:
So many amazing memories with Uncle D. Our time in Japan together will always hold a special place in my heart. 
.
Derek Ho was honored today at Pipeline -where he was king.  Hundreds if not over 1000 people gathered for a beautiful ceremony and paddle out to lay his ashes.  By official decree today is officially now Derek K Ho day in Hawaii!! 
.
Always love you Uncle Derek and the entire Ho Ohana. 
.
 #aloha #alohaderekho #derekkhoday #rainbow @freesurfmag @derekho1980 #surfing

node.title: The legendary Derek Ho, Hawaii’s first world champion!!!

node.text:
to @skudinsurfad at @americandream !!! I don’t think there is anywhere in the world you can be surfing perfect waves and then 20 minutes later snowboarding down a mountain. @americandream has made it a reality. Anyone wanting to learn how to surf or snowboard this is the place!!!! Thanks 📷 @jaybelsky for the quick edit. Very much appreciated!!!
.
.
.
@thule @rhone @volcom @skudinsurf @whitewaterwilly @mokuhawaii
.
.
.
#bringyourlife #bringyourkids #surf #snowboard #snowboardkids #surfkids #gromlife #barrelmcnamara

node.text:
At first I was speechless. Really had no idea what to say. Literally this is a dream come true. Greater than my wildest dreams. Then it hit me … none of this is possible without a TEAM. Your team is everyone you surround yourself with and soooo many people made this possible !!!! So many people believed in me and Nazare. So many have dedicated their life to seeing this dream become a reality!!! Thank you to everyone who was apart of this. Every positive thought from everyone around the world made this happen!!! THANK YOU!!
.
.
#100ftwave @hbomax #nazare #portugal #bigwavesurfing #surfing #dreams #foreverforward #thulecrew #bringyourlife 
.
@dinocasimiro @cristopisco @mercedesbenz_pt @thule @karlwiedemann @k_p_lee1758 @rawelementsusa @andrew_cotty @al_mennie @sharpxxl @mrs.katiegordon @aloha_pablo @quince_sf @ricksalomon @xhapeland @rustypreisendorfer @staycovered @futuresfins @rhone @astralfootwear @fe.earthtobody #markbell @rinaldiwave @cramminfair @alexvonfurstenberg @brandon_schlesinger #bert #pitbull @elgrancejota @joelewis @theenvironet @sarofima and so so so many more!! @sylvia.cdmelo @cynthiarowley @daniriediker @patrickseabase @rail2rail @pauhanasurfsupply @bjorn2bmild @mamaunearthed

node.text:
It’s finally happening!!! After the blood, sweat and tears of 
countless people, not to mention the hopes and dreams of many we are so honored and proud to share this life long dream and journey with all of you. July 18th!!!! See you there. 
.

A lifelong odyssey. One impossible dream.
#100FootWave , an @HBO original documentary series that captures Garrett McNamara’s legacy as a surfing pioneer that inspired a new generation of giant wave riders, premiering July 18 at 10PM on @HBOMax.
.
@andrew_cotty @sharpxxl @lucaschumbo @elgrancejota @kai_lenny @justinedupont33 @mamaunearthed @rhone @rawelementsusa @thule @thule_adventure @astralfootwear @fe.earthtobody  @futuresfins @mercedesbenz @mercedesbenz_pt @yamahamarineportugal @yamahamarineeu @linobogalho

I honestly wasn’t sure if he was going fall in love with surfing. All he use to want to do is fish. Now all he wants to do is #surf !!! And man I wish I had his style at that age. .
.
.

node.text:
Without this planet we will all die. It is time we unite for the the greater good of humanity. Together we can make a difference. Every time you spend even a $1 you are either promoting the current single us plastic situation or protesting it. Every time you put food in your mouth you are either supporting local, organic agriculture or you are supporting deforestation, poisoned soil and a plethora of other challenges. Every moment of every day you are making a choice. So if you a celebrating EARTH DAY then make a commitment to make earth day choices every day!!!
.
.
.
#foreverforward #bringyourlife #bringyourkids #getoutside #earthfocus #earthday2021 
.
.
.
@thule @mercedesbenz_pt @astralfootwear @rhone @rawelementsusa @fe.earthtobody @cymbiotika @futuresfins @yamahamarineeu

Even if you aren’t on #oahu all it takes is a little research to find ways to #shoplocal and only buy items NOT in plastic!!! We can do this. VOTE with your dollar. Go plant based and if that’s too much go #plantbased six days a week. It’s not just good for your health but good for the planet. We can use that land to grow food for humans instead of cows!!!! Thank you @themylkbarn 
.
.
.
#plantbased #plantbasednutrition  #plantbasedvegan

node.text:
This year is definitely not what most of us had in mind but we sure have had a blast making the best of it. The easiest way to make lemonade out of lemons is surrounding yourself with incredible humans who make life worth living??? TAG your humans that make life inspiring and FUN!!!
.
.
.
We are so blessed to have so many incredible people in our lives. The list goes on forever but to name a few that made this video possible ... @luisbendesa incredible filming talent. @elgrancejota energy, @cynthiarowley @pauhanasurfsupply @theeddieaikau @haleiwabowls @rail2rail @jocelyne_barnes @easternskateboardsupply @rustysurfboards @xhapeland @rhone @propelskateboardsforkids @yamahamarineportugal @yamahamarineit @yamahamotoreu @oceanramsey @juansharks @theenvironet @flowhive @snorkelhottubs @bodyglove @watermanunlimited @mercedesbenz @mercedesbenz_pt @buondioficial @thule @rawelementsusa 
.
.
.
#foreverforward #wheninrhone #hawaiilife #hawaiifamily #thulecrew

node.text:
PORTUGAL here we come. 
.
We are going the long way via Seattle, San Fran, Newark, Iceland and then our happy place, where we feel most ourselves … NAZARE!!!
.
Going to make the best of the long journey and visit with amazing friends and see the beauty in everything. It is so easy to get frustrated and annoyed, especially traveling during these times but you can always find something good if you are looking for good!!!
📷 @vasco_estrelado_photographer 
.
#travelingwithkids #travelingwithbaby #portugal #nazare #bringyourlife #bringyourkids #thulecrew

node.text:
We decided to let the UNIVERSE decide our DESTINY and there seems to be one more soul that wants to call us Mom and Dad. There is a bun in the oven and we will get to meet the baby in December when I deliver it in Portugal 🤪 Yup… it will be our first Portuguese born baby. Any of my Portuguese friends out there please share your recommendation on everything  baby and to EVERYONE out there we are taking baby name suggestions!!! Please give us your best … we like goddess names, and names with special meanings from other cultures. We like UNIQUE because at the end of the day each one of us is a snowflake… completely different and special!!!
.
Thank you @goldielockshawaii @paulizakmusic and 📷 @nikiizak for making these photos possible!!!
.
.
#bunintheoven #babyonboard #portugalbaby #waterbabies #hawaii #hawaiilifestyle #oceanbaby #maternityphotoshoot #swimmingwithdolphins🐬 #wilddolphins #hawaiidolphins #swimmingwithwilddolphins

node.text:
SAFTEY FIRST… I know most people think I’m crazy but I like to say I’m CALCULATED crazy. I really only do what I’m comfortable with and I definitely asses the risk. In everything we do there are ways to mitigate the danger associated. Yes sometimes accidents happen and sometimes a split second decision can lead to the worse. This SUNDAY we see one of those moments. 
.
#100ftwave #nazare #portugal #bigwaves #bigwavesurfing #wipeout #dangerzone #safteyfirst

node.text:
TRUST…. The most important thing to trust in life is the universe. If you stay present, are a good person, with good intentions the universe will guide you. My greatest lesson has been to not fight the universe but to listen… especially listen to CLOSED DOORS, those have the most wisdom and OPPORTUNITY. Every closed door is an opportunity for something bigger and better for your life. It might feel crummy in the moment but just know in your bones that something better is coming along. 
.
#bringyourlife #bringyourkids #thulecrew #getoutsideandplay #getoutsideandexplore #natureismedicine #hiddenopportunities

node.text:
So wrong it’s right !!!
The 4 o’clock bomb came at 5:00

@matahidrollet paddle or tow hands down the BEST AT CHOOP’S 🙌🙌🙌
Congrats again brother. 
I remember meeting you as a young boy when you were with Raimana on the @apple shoot and he was working with you like a big brother. It was awesome to see your brother @manoa_drollet take you out there and wait nine hours for the wave of the day. Your brother was always the one that got the wave of the day and now you are. 

Matahi Drollet is no stranger to giant Teahupoo. His older brother Manoa (along with Raimana Van Bastolaer) was among the first crew to really charge here over a decade ago; Manoa was also the one towing Matahi yesterday, during one of the biggest swells to hit that bit of reef since Code Red in 2011. Drollet played the patience game, which paid off around 5pm, right before sunset, as the swell peaked and he was whipped in the perfect spot by his brother and took the perfect line through an impossibly heavy, crazy loud, building-sized tube — and straight into surf history. Stay tuned for more coverage. 

🎥 @timmckenna 
@10barrelbrewing

node.text:
This is TAHITI right NOW!!! Normally I would be on suicide watch right now if I missed this swell and had the capabilities of being there. Somehow I am completely content being at home. Don’t get me wrong I’d love to be there but it’s not the end of the world. Biggest bomb usually comes around 4… let’s see what comes in an hour!!! Pray that everyone comes home and in one piece!!
.

Report -> Friday, August 13 2021 🤯
🎥 @hinateaboosie @heimiti.fierro 
MONSTERWAVE ! It’s HUGE !! XL size SSW swell TOW ONLY !! watch out guys 😱 Far from my island and without being able to shoot this impression swell, I see behind my live screen @kaulivaast take the biggest wave of his life !! #hardballs brother 
To the aquatic photographers who were in the water during this massive wave, I hope everyone is safe 🙏 

The videos are not mine, thanks to the girls for sharing :
Video 1 @hinateaboosie 
Video 2 @heimiti.fierro 
Video 3 camera hosted by Havae Bungalows
.
#teahupoo #tahiti #monsterwaves #bigwaves #bigwavesurfing #surfing

node.text:
HAPPY BIRTHDAY to my amazing husband Garrett!!! I am sooooo glad he was born and that our two souls collided. It wasn’t the best timing but there was no stopping our love and the collective mission of making the world a better place. This PHOTO was taken during @surfershealing #puertorico !!! That is NOT our child. It is one of the many kids who gets to experience the ocean and surfing through Surfers Healing. The first time we ever laid eyes on each other was at a Surfers Healing event. Surfing and the ocean brought us together. The ocean has given us everything we have and I believe the ocean has made Garrett who he is. HAPPY BIRTHDAY to the most charismatic, loving, caring, thoughtful man!!! You keep life light and fun. So excited to spend the next 50 years with you!!!
.
#happybirthday #surfershealing #surftherapy #theearlydays #jobosbeach #garrettmcnamara #surfing

node.text:
FLASHBACK to that one time @mamaunearthed had to fly with a drugged invalid!!! Funny but not funny. (Check out last picture)
.
AND to @frank_quirarte_photo our angel who stood by our side. We truly don’t know how we would have made it through those two days without you!!! 
.
To our friends who houses us when we needed a safe place after surgery @kredford7 and @jred5562 !!! Thank you for being their and being a bright light. 
.
To my brother @liam__mcnamara for not even hesitating to help me find someone to piece me back together. We would have been lost without your guidance and quickness. 
.
To everyone who sent even the tiniest bit of healing energy our way!! Thank you. 
.
#flashbacks #100ftwave #garrettmcnamara #mavericks #wipeout
